The inline comments are a little repetitive here I think, they seem to repeat the `enum` level comment. Consider doing something like:


```dart
/// Specifies between 2 thumbs in a [RangeSlider].
///
/// In LTR text direction, the [start] thumb is the left-most thumb and the [end]
/// thumb is the right-most thumb. In RTL text direction the [start] thumb is the
/// right-most thumb, and the [end] thumb is the left-most thumb.
enum Thumb {
  /// Left-most thumb in LTR, otherwise, right-most thumb.
  start,

   /// Right-most thumb in LTR, otherwise, left-most thumb.
  end
}
```

This still repeats the same info, but is slightly less repetitive.

